Sub Kill_Excel()
  Dim oShell : Set oShell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
  oShell.Run "taskkill /f /t /im excel.exe ", , True
End Sub
Sub Kill_TaxFile()
  Dim oShell : Set oShell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
  oShell.Run "taskkill /f /t /im paycor_taxfile.exe ", , True
End Sub
